snippet.title: SLICK SLIME SAM - DIY, Comedy, Science
snippet.description:
Have you ever seen a talking slime? Here he is – Slick Slime Sam! He is pink, he is hilarious, he will die for candy and he always makes sure you are having a good time while watching his adventures.

This is an official channel for the most entertaining slime in history! He and his "pet human" Sue make the most bizarre DIYs, cook incredible foods together and bicker endlessly to find common ground.

Subscribe to Sam's channel and give some thumbs-up and he will make more videos to brighten up your day!


Shop our awesome t-shirts, pop sockets, and more follow the links below
